    <h1 class="text-display-s mb-24">Design System</h1>
    <div class="stack stack--16">
      <p class="text-body-lg">This design system provides a single source of truth for the Regent's University London digital presence.</p>
      <h2 class="text-h3">Tech Stack</h2>
      <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: var(--sp-24);" class="stack stack--8">
        <li class="text-body"><strong>SCSS</strong> — Variables, nesting, mixins with zero runtime cost</li>
        <li class="text-body"><strong>Nunjucks</strong> — Logic-light HTML templating</li>
        <li class="text-body"><strong>Eleventy</strong> — Static site generator, zero client JS</li>
        <li class="text-body"><strong>Vite</strong> — Dev server with fast HMR</li>
        <li class="text-body"><strong>Style Dictionary</strong> — Token pipeline: SCSS + CSS vars + JSON</li>
      </ul>
      <h2 class="text-h3">The Five Layers</h2>
      <ol style="list-style: decimal; padding-left: var(--sp-24);" class="stack stack--8">
        <li class="text-body"><strong>Foundation</strong> — Design tokens</li>
        <li class="text-body"><strong>Components</strong> — SCSS + JS + Nunjucks per component</li>
        <li class="text-body"><strong>Layouts</strong> — Grid and structural spacing</li>
        <li class="text-body"><strong>Templates</strong> — Page shells</li>
        <li class="text-body"><strong>Pages</strong> — Fully assembled pages</li>
      </ol>
